01:33:03.240 --> 01:33:05.880
me just do this first.

01:33:05.880 --> 01:33:08.560
Let's take tau again.

01:33:08.560 --> 01:33:10.300
Take r equal to tangent rho.

01:33:10.300 --> 01:33:13.710
Rho is some other coordinate.

01:33:13.710 --> 01:33:15.400
And r from 0 to infinity.

01:33:15.400 --> 01:33:21.170
Then rho would be from
