01:33:21.170 --> 01:33:22.900
OK?

01:33:22.900 --> 01:33:26.050
0 to pi over 2.

01:33:26.050 --> 01:33:31.530
And you park this into
here with a little bit

01:33:31.530 --> 01:33:36.980
tiny-- so after two seconds,
