01:34:16.660 --> 01:34:18.830
So this is just a cylinder.

01:34:18.830 --> 01:34:22.384
So this is just a cylinder.

01:34:22.384 --> 01:34:23.356
Let me draw it here.

01:34:35.020 --> 01:34:36.200
So this is a cylinder.

01:34:44.510 --> 01:34:46.520
OK?

01:34:46.520 --> 01:34:48.670
So this direction
can be considered--

01:34:48.670 --> 01:34:53.895
the radial direction
