01:35:04.530 --> 01:35:09.794
And this direction is
the omega d minus 1,

01:35:09.794 --> 01:35:11.210
or the polar
coordinate direction.

01:35:11.210 --> 01:35:14.660
I'm only drawing one of them.

01:35:14.660 --> 01:35:17.270
OK?

01:35:17.270 --> 01:35:20.740
So essentially, this I have
a structure of a cylinder.

01:35:20.740 --> 01:35:24.630
And at the center here,
I have rho equal to 0.

01:35:24.630 --> 01:35:28.290
And here, I have rho
