01:35:28.290 --> 01:35:29.010
OK?

01:35:29.010 --> 01:35:31.832
Took rho from 0 to pi over 2.

01:35:31.832 --> 01:35:32.790
OK?

01:35:32.790 --> 01:35:37.660
And when you go to pi over 2,
