01:35:57.860 --> 01:36:00.100
OK?

01:36:00.100 --> 01:36:03.010
Is this clear?

01:36:03.010 --> 01:36:04.390
So pi over 2 is the boundary.

01:36:04.390 --> 01:36:05.870
Now the boundary map.

