01:36:27.920 --> 01:36:28.590
OK?

01:36:28.590 --> 01:36:30.914
So the boundary itself,
it's-- so the boundary itself,

01:36:30.914 --> 01:36:31.580
it's a cylinder.

01:36:31.580 --> 01:36:33.770
The whole space is
