takes only pi over 2

01:39:08.651 --> 01:39:10.150
for light ray to
reach the boundary.

01:39:13.300 --> 01:39:13.800
OK?

01:39:13.800 --> 01:39:16.840
Because rho only
goes from pi over 2,

01:39:16.840 --> 01:39:20.490
and light ray always
travel in 45 degrees.

01:39:20.490 --> 01:39:23.060
So this is just like-- if
