01:39:32.560 --> 01:39:34.880
And then you reach the boundary.

01:39:34.880 --> 01:39:36.370
And then take log of pi over 2.

01:39:36.370 --> 01:39:37.920
Yeah, so this is pi over 2.

01:39:37.920 --> 01:39:39.010
So this is tau equal to 0.

01:39:39.010 --> 01:39:48.710
And then this would be
