01:40:23.000 --> 01:40:27.240
If you follow that,
then that equals 1

01:40:27.240 --> 01:40:30.790
into precisely one period
of the light ray traveling.

01:40:30.790 --> 01:40:31.370
OK?

01:40:31.370 --> 01:40:35.150
But the key thing is that the
light ray will travel pi over 2

01:40:35.150 --> 01:40:38.044
to the boundary.

01:40:38.044 --> 01:40:38.960
And now you can check.

01:40:38.960 --> 01:40:42.510
If you look at--
