01:41:00.632 --> 01:41:02.090
So this is a massive particle.

01:41:09.380 --> 01:41:13.890
So the massive particle will
never reach the boundary.

01:41:13.890 --> 01:41:19.550
It will always be
reflected back intuitively,

01:41:19.550 --> 01:41:22.770
