01:41:22.770 --> 01:41:23.420
OK?

01:41:23.420 --> 01:41:25.770
So you will show
this fact yourself.

01:41:25.770 --> 01:41:29.380
And your P-set show that
actually the massive particle

01:41:29.380 --> 01:41:32.790
will never reach the boundary.

01:41:32.790 --> 01:41:42.460
So in a sense, so if you
look at this metric, at rho

01:41:42.460 --> 01:41:48.520
equal to 0, at rho equal
to 0, this is essentially

01:41:48.520 --> 01:41:49.350
like a flat metric.

01:41:49.350 --> 01:41:52.530
Because at rho equal to
0, this is just a sphere.

01:41:52.530 --> 01:41:53.390
So this becomes 1.

01:41:53.390 --> 01:41:55.950
This is a sphere.

01:41:55.950 --> 01:41:57.450
Yeah.

01:41:57.450 --> 01:41:58.290
Yeah.

01:41:58.290 --> 01:42:02.630
Rho equal to 0, this is
