01:42:09.850 --> 01:42:11.290
And then you have a time.

01:42:11.290 --> 01:42:13.160
And then this scale
factor becomes 1.

01:42:13.160 --> 01:42:16.080
So at rho equal to 0, just like
you have ordinary Minkowski

01:42:16.080 --> 01:42:18.080
spacetime.

01:42:18.080 --> 01:42:23.410
And then the curvature comes
in when you go to finite rho,

01:42:23.410 --> 01:42:25.786
