01:42:30.690 --> 01:42:31.650
travel to the boundary.

01:42:31.650 --> 01:42:32.150
OK?

01:42:32.150 --> 01:42:33.600
Always reflected back.

01:42:33.600 --> 01:42:36.280
In some sense, you can think
